    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>Some such Butterfly be seen<br>\nOn Brazilian Pampas --<br>\nJust at noon -- no later -- Sweet --<br>\nThen -- the License closes --\n</p>\n<p>Some such Spice -- express and pass --<br>\nSubject to Your Plucking --<br>\nAs the Stars -- You knew last Night --<br>\nForeigners -- This Morning --\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
