    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>Peace is a fiction of our Faith --<br>\nThe Bells a Winter Night<br>\nBearing the Neighbor out of Sound<br>\nThat never did alight.\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
