    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>I hide myself within my flower,<br>\nThat fading from your Vase,<br>\nYou, unsuspecting, feel for me --<br>\nAlmost a loneliness.\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
