    "type": "poetry",
    "subtitle": "A Classic Poem",
    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>I'm \"wife\" -- I've finished that --<br>\nThat other state --<br>\nI'm Czar -- I'm \"Woman\" now --<br>\nIt's safer so --\n</p>\n<p>How odd the Girl's life looks<br>\nBehind this soft Eclipse --<br>\nI think that Earth feels so<br>\nTo folks in Heaven -- now --\n</p>\n<p>This being comfort -- then<br>\nThat other kind -- was pain --<br>\nBut why compare?<br>\nI'm \"Wife\"! Stop there!\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
