    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>No Autumn's intercepting Chill<br>\nAppalls this Tropic Breast --<br>\nBut African Exuberance<br>\nAnd Asiatic rest.\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
