    "title": "The butterfly obtains",
    "author": "Emily Dickinson",
    "type": "poetry",
    "subtitle": "A Classic Poem",
    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>The butterfly obtains<br>\nBut little sympathy<br>\nThough favorably mentioned<br>\nIn Entomology --\n</p>\n<p>Because he travels freely<br>\nAnd wears a proper coat<br>\nThe circumspect are certain<br>\nThat he is dissolute --\n</p>\n<p>Had he the homely scutcheon<br>\nOf modest Industry<br>\n'Twere fitter certifying<br>\nFor Immortality --\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
