    "title": "Oh Sumptuous moment",
    "author": "Emily Dickinson",
    "type": "poetry",
    "subtitle": "A Classic Poem",
    "bgImage": "url(./images/bg-dickinson.jpg)",
    "content": "<p>Oh Sumptuous moment<br>\nSlower go<br>\nThat I may gloat on thee --<br>\n'Twill never be the same to starve<br>\nNow I abundance see --\n</p>\n<p>Which was to famish, then or now --<br>\nThe difference of Day<br>\nAsk him unto the Gallows led --<br>\nWith morning in the sky --\n</p>\n<br>\n<p><em>Tags: poetry, classic, dickinson, american</em></p>"
